    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood of the species Carya tomentosa, native to the United States. It is used for tool handles, sporting goods, turnery, and vehicle bodies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
